Airworthiness Directives; Saab Model SAAB SF340A and SAAB 340B Airplanes, 
Equipped With Flight Equipment and Engineering Limited Model 121 Series Seats 


<AGENCY>
AGENCY:

 Federal Aviation Administration, DOT. 


</AGENCY>
<ACTION>
ACTION:

